Resize Images on Upload - FREE v1.0.0 for OpenCart

Increases image upload max filesize and automatically resizes images on filemanager upload in Admin dashboard panel.

Default Settings:
- max filesize 2MB (2000kb)
- automatically resize images > 900px width or height down to 900px by 900px

Settings can be edited by manually updating the vQmod file.

Looking for a more user-friendly configuration option panel and/or need to set additional restrictions on the image such as dimension, filetype, and length of filename? Please see the full/premium version, Resize Images on Upload + Plus (http://www.opencart.com/index.php?route=extension/extension/info&extension_id=11497).
	
Requirements: OpenCart v1.5.0-1.5.6 with vQmod installed


